metadata.name: Rare Lazy Apepes #2
metadata.description: Rare Lazy Apepes is a community based project brought to you by a team of 2 amazing people (if we do say so ourselves).“R.L.A City ” is a reference to our leadership team who are here to help the R.L.A. community along the way as we continue to grow. Each team member brings knowledge and expertise creating a new and fun experience like no other! From artwork to event planning. Transparent communication to team building. Design to community growth. From dreams to reality…all this to say…this project has one thing in mind, growing with YOU!R.L.A City is here to help lead the community in the right way R.L.A way (Where community is government )Note: We are independent creators and are not affiliated with Yuga Labs , BAYC,LAZY LIONS, RAYC, MAYC,LAYC NOR Rarelabs.
